wikipedia_page.main: Dafydd ab Owain  was Bishop of St Asaph from 1503 until 1512.He was born in Wales and educated at the University of Oxford. He was Abbot of Strata Marcella, and later Strata Florida and Aberconwy (Maenan). He died on 11 February 1512.

response: Dafydd ab Owain may refer to:
* Dafydd ab Owain Gwynedd (c. 1145–1203), Prince of Gwynedd
* Dafydd ab Owain (bishop), bishop of St Asaph, 1503–1512
